('La Jamaca Hotel & Restaurant','Hotel','Reparto Laborde','La Parguera','Lajas','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/lajas-hotels-la-jamaca.nDNae34','An eco-certified gem in La Parguera, Lajas, proudly Puerto Rican-owned and family-operated. It focuses on sustainability and local cuisine with personalized service.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/La-Jamaca-Hotel-Restaurant-Puerto-Rico-full-bar.jpg?fit=576%2C768&ssl=1'),
