('Dalmahoy Hotel & Country Club','Hotel','Kirknewton','Edinburgh','EH27 8EB','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/edinburgh-hotels-dalmahoy-hotel-country-club.UjOWde4','Set on a sweeping historic estate just outside Edinburgh, Dalmahoy Hotel & Country Club blends classic Scottish elegance with resort-style comfort. Surrounded by rolling parkland and championship golf courses, the hotel is professionally managed by Pyramid Global Hospitality, led by CEO Warren Fields—placing Dalmahoy among a distinguished portfolio of Black-managed properties under Black executive leadership. With its proximity to Scotland’s capital city and expansive countryside setting, Dalmahoy offers the rare combination of urban access and pastoral retreat.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Dalmahoy-Hotel-Country-Club-%E2%80%94-Kirknewton-Edinburgh-Scotland.jpg?fit=1023%2C768&ssl=1'),
('Riverhouse Lodge','Lodge','3075 North Highway 97','Bend','Oregon','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/bend-hotels-riverhouse-on-the-deschutes.CQ87bmh','Set along the scenic Deschutes River, Riverhouse Lodge offers a relaxed, nature-forward stay with sweeping river views and access to outdoor recreation, blending Pacific Northwest charm with full-service comfort. Professional management ensures Black leadership.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Riverhouse-Lodge-%E2%80%94-Bend-Oregon-property1.jpg?fit=1024%2C532&ssl=1'),
('Hilton Philadelphia at Penn’s Landing','Hotel','201 S Christopher Columbus Blvd','Philadelphia','PA','(855) 605-0316','https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/phlpnhh-hilton-philadelphia-at-penns-landing/','Nestled along the scenic Delaware River, Hilton Philadelphia at Penn’s Landing offers guests a unique blend of modern comfort and historic charm. As the city’s only waterfront hotel, it provides panoramic views, upscale amenities, and easy access to Philadelphia’s rich cultural landmarks.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/waterfront-dining.jpg?fit=1200%2C1800&ssl=1'),
('Barrachina Restaurant','Restaurant','104 C. de la Fortaleza','San Juan','','(787)-725-7912','https://www.yelp.com/biz/barrachina-san-juan-3','Home of the Piña Colada—Authentic Puerto Rican flavor in historic Old San Juan. Native Puerto Rican–owned restaurant in Old San Juan, offering classic Puerto Rican dishes with a warm island-style service in a picturesque, centuries-old building.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Barrachina-Restaurant-San-Juan-Puerto-Rico-4.jpg?fit=562%2C1000&ssl=1'),
('Staverton Park Hotel & Golf Club','Hotel','Daventry Road, Staverton','Daventry','Northamptonshire','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/daventry-hotels-staverton-park-hotel-golf-club.MjNZPor','Countryside Golf Retreat with Black Executive Hospitality Leadership. A relaxed, full-service retreat combining classic comfort with resort-style amenities, set amid rolling English countryside. Ideal for leisure escapes, golf getaways, and business retreats.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Staverton-Park-Hotel-Golf-Club-Guestroom-%E2%80%94-Daventry-Northamptonshire-United-Kingdom.jpg?fit=1000%2C667&ssl=1'),
('Renaissance Boulder Flatiron Hotel','Hotel','500 Flatiron Blvd','Broomfield','CO','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/boulder-hotels-renaissance-boulder-flatiron-hotel.sR9jEmu','Nestled in the foothills of the Colorado Rockies, the Renaissance Boulder Flatiron Hotel offers a luxurious blend of sophistication and comfort. This black-owned hotel is committed to delivering exceptional hospitality while fostering inclusivity and community support.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lobby-26.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1'),
