('Colorado Springs Marriott','Hotel','5580 Tech Center Dr','Colorado Springs','CO','N/A','https://expedia.com/affiliates/colorado-springs-hotels-colorado-springs-marriott.XNNbtyh','Nestled at the base of the majestic Rocky Mountains, Colorado Springs Marriott offers a luxurious retreat for travelers seeking a balance of comfort, sophistication, and breathtaking natural scenery. This black-owned hotel in Colorado Springs delivers exceptional service and a warm, welcoming atmosphere.','https://blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-color-268-png-vr-1.png'),
('Black Orchid Resort','Boutique Resort','#2 Dawson Lane','Burrell Boom Village','Belize District','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/burrell-boom-hotels-black-orchid-resort.Aha3IRm','A riverside jungle retreat where tranquil nature meets warm Belizean hospitality. Black Orchid Resort is a Black-owned, family-operated boutique resort blending lush jungle scenery with warm, personalized service. It is recognized as one of Belize’s respected inland retreats, offering a peaceful setting with riverfront views and abundant wildlife.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Black-Orchid-Resort-%E2%80%94-Burrell-Boom-Belize-dron-view.jpg?fit=1024%2C768&ssl=1'),
('Fort Lauderdale Marriott North','Hotel','6650 N Andrews Ave','Fort Lauderdale','FL','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/fort-lauderdale-hotels-fort-lauderdale-marriott-north.XKKeVIk','The Fort Lauderdale Marriott North offers a refreshing blend of style, convenience, and thoughtful service—managed by Pyramid Global Hospitality, a major hotel management firm led by trailblazing Black CEO Warren Fields. Located near Florida’s scenic Intracoastal Waterway, this contemporary hotel serves as a welcoming hub for business and leisure travelers alike, delivering elevated experiences for guests from all walks of life.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Fort-Lauderdale-Marriott-North-11.jpg?fit=1024%2C683&ssl=1'),
('Residence Inn by Marriott Boulder Longmont','Hotel','1450 Dry Creek Dr','Longmont','CO','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/boulder-hotels-residence-inn-by-marriott-boulder-longmont.cYzx1iC','Comfortable Extended Stays with a Scenic Backdrop. This black-owned hotel provides the perfect combination of home-like comfort and modern convenience for extended stays or weekend getaways.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/market-11.jpg?fit=1200%2C800&ssl=1'),
('Paradise Cove Resort','Resort','Paradise Dr','The Cove','Anguilla','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/cove-bay-hotels-paradise-cove-resort.LCwZ727','Nestled on the breathtaking shores of Anguilla, Paradise Cove Resort is a Black-owned tropical retreat that offers the perfect blend of relaxation, luxury, and island charm. This intimate, all-suite resort is just minutes from the world-famous Rendezvous Bay, providing guests with spacious accommodations, lush gardens, and warm Caribbean hospitality. Whether you''re seeking a romantic getaway, a family vacation, or a peaceful retreat, Paradise Cove delivers an unforgettable island experience.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/beach-house.jpg?fit=1000%2C617&ssl=1'),
('Saddlebrook Resort','Resort','5700 Saddlebrook Way','Wesley Chapel','Florida','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/tampa-hotels-saddlebrook-golf-resort-and-spa.z8oOlVm','Premier Sports & Wellness Destination with Black Leadership. Known as a training ground for champions and a retreat for active travelers, the resort blends upscale accommodations with championship golf, elite tennis facilities, wellness experiences, and a full complement of resort amenities.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Saddlebrook-Resort-in-Wesley-Chapel-property.jpg?fit=1024%2C576&ssl=1'),
('Jamaican Mi Hungry','Restaurant','225 Centre St','Jamaica Plain','MA','(617)-708-0465','https://www.jamaicamihungry.com/','Jamaican Mi Hungry is a celebrated Black-owned restaurant in Boston, Massachusetts, offering authentic Jamaican cuisine. Founded by Chef Ernie Campbell in 2012, the establishment has evolved from a private chef service into a full-service catering company, food truck, and brick-and-mortar restaurant.','https://blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/3-color-268-png-vr-1.png'),
('Marley Resort & Spa','Resort','West Bay Street','Nassau','New Providence Island','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/nassau-hotels-marley-resort-spa.BQQeVwP','Experience a truly iconic Caribbean escape at Marley Resort & Spa, an oceanfront boutique retreat located on the world-famous Cable Beach in Nassau, Bahamas. Once the private vacation home of reggae legend Bob Marley and Rita Marley, this historic estate has been transformed into an intimate luxury resort that blends Afro-Caribbean design, holistic wellness, and the unmistakable rhythm of reggae culture.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Marley-Resort-Spa-Nassau-Bahamas-.jpg?fit=1200%2C900&ssl=1'),
('iKhaya Lodge & Conference Centre','Hotel','Dunkley Square','Cape Town','Western Cape','','https://expedia.com/affiliates/cape-town-hotels-ikhaya-lodge-conference-centre.YGQLpe6','Located in the heart of Cape Town, iKhaya Lodge is a Black-owned hotel in South Africa that offers a warm, welcoming atmosphere infused with African design, culture, and hospitality. Perched on the slopes of Table Mountain, this intimate lodge provides breathtaking views of the city and an immersive experience that highlights local craftsmanship and heritage.','https://i0.wp.com/blackhotelguide.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/iKhaya-Lodge.jpg?fit=1200%2C797&ssl=1')
)
INSERT INTO public.businesses (name, business_name, category, address, city, state, phone, website, description, banner_url, owner_id, listing_status, is_verified)
SELECT s.business_name, s.business_name, s.category, NULLIF(s.address,''), NULLIF(s.city,''), NULLIF(s.state,''), NULLIF(s.phone,''), NULLIF(s.website,''), NULLIF(s.description,''), NULLIF(s.banner_url,''), 'bd72a75e-1310-4f40-9c74-380443b09d9b'::uuid, 'live', true
FROM src s
WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM public.businesses b WHERE lower(regexp_replace(b.business_name,'[^A-Za-z0-9]+','','g')) = lower(regexp_replace(s.business_name,'[^A-Za-z0-9]+','','g')));